headline: KEYBANK AND QOLO PARTNER TO ADVANCE COMMERCIAL BANKING CAPABILITIES WITH VIRTUAL ACCOUNT MANAGEMENT
summary: KeyBank (NYSE: KEY) today announced a strategic partnership with Qolo, a pioneer of payment cycle management solutions. This partnership, along with the launch of KeyVAM® announced last year, marks the most recent in KeyBank's decade-long strategy of investing in and partnering with emerging fintech providers.
